602
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,893
This is insane.

603
00:30:11,977 --> 00:30:13,311
Whoa…

604
00:30:13,395 --> 00:30:15,272
Lee Sobin is incredible.

605
00:30:15,355 --> 00:30:16,440
The survivor

606
00:30:17,065 --> 00:30:18,442
