607
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,945
Wow, one shot, one kill.

608
00:30:22,029 --> 00:30:24,197
-It was her first time.
-Yes, on her first try.

609
00:30:24,281 --> 00:30:26,742
- One shot, one kill.
- One shot, one kill.

610
00:30:27,951 --> 00:30:31,413
I think Sobin
will come in first of all the shamans.

611
00:30:32,205 --> 00:30:34,624
She's been a shaman for a long time.

612
00:30:34,708 --> 00:30:37,377
She has the confidence.
I think she'll win the whole thing.

613
00:30:39,796 --> 00:30:41,798
I'm excited to see her fortune-telling.

614
00:30:42,466 --> 00:30:44,092
