619
00:30:54,019 --> 00:30:55,937
- Because I'm just a novice.
- Right.

620
00:30:57,856 --> 00:31:02,194
I became a shaman
when I was 7 years old.

621
00:31:02,277 --> 00:31:07,407
My Guardian spirits are my Granny spirit
and the Child spirits.

622
00:31:07,491 --> 00:31:10,869
When I was young, none of my friends
could see the kids I saw.

623
00:31:10,952 --> 00:31:12,454
The kids were ghosts.

624
00:31:12,537 --> 00:31:16,166
Those young ghosts, the Child spirits,
are still my friends.

625
00:31:17,918 --> 00:31:20,462
I'll just go up and say
what my deities say.

626
00:31:21,922 --> 00:31:24,216
