640
00:32:06,675 --> 00:32:09,970
You never know the result until it's over.

641
00:32:13,181 --> 00:32:14,891
Rumi is certainly intimidating.

642
00:32:14,975 --> 00:32:16,184
She's a wide-eyed lunatic.

643
00:32:16,768 --> 00:32:21,231
♪ Riddle me this ♪

644
00:32:21,815 --> 00:32:24,359
