645
00:32:25,735 --> 00:32:27,279
Ta-da!

646
00:32:29,281 --> 00:32:32,325
Mmm! I feel good now.

647
00:32:33,076 --> 00:32:35,537
I'll show you
the ultimate sunshine energy.

648
00:32:36,288 --> 00:32:38,456
I'm one of those
wide-eyed maniacs, you know.

649
00:32:41,501 --> 00:32:43,003
I'm excited about Rumi.

650
00:32:43,086 --> 00:32:44,504
She's so bubbly.

651
00:32:45,088 --> 00:32:47,174
Wow. They're both so extraordinary.

652
00:32:47,674 --> 00:32:50,051
