654
00:33:02,022 --> 00:33:03,315
- Whoa.
- Whoa.

655
00:33:03,398 --> 00:33:04,816
She scared me.

656
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:05,942
Sorry.

657
00:33:06,651 --> 00:33:07,736
She's so innocent.

658
00:33:08,528 --> 00:33:10,405
- Her energy's damn strong.
- For sure.

659
00:33:10,488 --> 00:33:11,573
That's true madness.

660
00:33:11,656 --> 00:33:13,533
- You're right. True madness.
- Yes.

661
00:33:13,617 --> 00:33:15,702
Lee Sobin goes first.

662
00:33:15,785 --> 00:33:18,288
Rumi goes second.

663
00:33:18,371 --> 00:33:19,915
Lee Sobin,

664
00:33:19,998 --> 00:33:22,417
