traveling back and forth.

675
00:34:18,014 --> 00:34:19,975
- My gosh.
- That's actually true.

676
00:34:20,058 --> 00:34:21,851
Her whole family moved abroad.

677
00:34:21,935 --> 00:34:22,936
1998, AGED 10
FAMILY MOVED TO THE US

678
00:34:24,062 --> 00:34:26,231
I moved to the US

679
00:34:26,314 --> 00:34:28,400
when I was in elementary school

680
00:34:28,483 --> 00:34:32,362
and moved back to Korea
about 15 years ago.

681
00:34:32,445 --> 00:34:34,572
Another thing.

682
00:34:34,656 --> 00:34:39,244
You seem really innocent,
cheerful, pretty,

683
00:34:39,327 --> 00:34:40,870
-and bright.
-Cheep, cheep.

684
00:34:42,706 --> 00:34:45,667
I hope Sobin
doesn't get distracted by her antics.

685
00:34:46,668 --> 00:34:50,213
You may seem
cheerful and happy all the time,

686
00:34:50,297 --> 00:34:52,132
but you're a very serious person.

687
00:34:52,215 --> 00:34:54,676
