"She has the brains. She's serious."

688
00:34:54,759 --> 00:34:57,220
- A compliment!
- Yes.

689
00:34:57,304 --> 00:35:00,849
I think you'll live a good life
if you use those smarts.

690
00:35:01,516 --> 00:35:03,977
She really is smart.
She got gifted education.

691
00:35:04,060 --> 00:35:05,562
- Did she?
- Yes.

692
00:35:05,645 --> 00:35:08,398
1990-91, AGED 2-3, COULD READ AND WRITE
AND WAS IN A GIFTED PROGRAM

693
00:35:08,481 --> 00:35:11,484
From what I'm hearing,

694
00:35:11,568 --> 00:35:14,529
